  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <i>Herogue</i>! Customize the perfect team and forge your way to victory in this turn-based, roguelike battler!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>One-of-a-kind mechanics</i></strong>: Each character has their own unique mechanics. Customize the fighting style that's best for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Upgrades</i></strong>: Use EXP coins to upgrade characters. Choose from an array of enhancement paths, allowing you to cultivate multiple styles for the same character. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Build a Team</strong></i>: Based on your strategy and likes, customize your team whenever you see fit. Who knows how a few tweaks will affect the whole team? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build a Poison-focused strategy, eliminating all enemies through poison effects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or go for a Power build, stacking buffs to unleash devastating bursts of damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or perhaps a Thorns strategy, relying on counterattacks to handle every threat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/e2209f2249c5f532cff6166739f94cae.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/e2209f2249c5f532cff6166739f94cae.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/e2209f2249c5f532cff6166739f94cae.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Tons of Statuses & Buffs</strong></i>: With tons of buffs, debuffs, and statuses floating around, they may be the key to victory...or defeat! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/18a819565971850d565bc987be04f23f.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/18a819565971850d565bc987be04f23f.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/18a819565971850d565bc987be04f23f.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Tag Team Mechanics</i></strong>: Deploy teammates from the sidelines to swap positions with characters currently in battle. Switch up the formation and turn the tides of victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b0a6f195f4f39ddfc7eaba994a8db176.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b0a6f195f4f39ddfc7eaba994a8db176.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b0a6f195f4f39ddfc7eaba994a8db176.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Not to mention all the other combinations and formations just waiting to be discovered!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <i>Herogue</i>! Customize the perfect team and forge your way to victory in this turn-based, roguelike battler!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong>: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>One-of-a-kind mechanics</i></strong>: Each character has their own unique mechanics. Customize the fighting style that's best for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Upgrades</i></strong>: Use EXP coins to upgrade characters. Choose from an array of enhancement paths, allowing you to cultivate multiple styles for the same character. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/22063e6931bd4ef13059293f84481239.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Build a Team</strong></i>: Based on your strategy and likes, customize your team whenever you see fit. Who knows how a few tweaks will affect the whole team? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/b9d2b5439dc21ffe012d0d2708a615ee.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build a Poison-focused strategy, eliminating all enemies through poison effects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/be0cee359c6111594b0facf4853fc4cc.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or go for a Power build, stacking buffs to unleash devastating bursts of damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.poster.avif?t=1743790618\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.webm?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067270/extras/9046f9627e9e95ea4a2a1b2a6a9520d7.mp4?t=1743790618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or perhaps a Thorns strategy, relying on counterattacks to handle every threat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shar